SELECT "atk_jadwal"."id", "atk_jadwal"."tahun", "atk_jadwal"."pengajuan_mulai", "atk_jadwal"."pengajuan_selesai", "atk_jadwal"."status", "atk_jadwal"."keterangan", "atk_jadwal"."updated", "atk_jadwal"."created" FROM "atk_jadwal" WHERE "atk_jadwal"."tahun" = ? ORDER BY "atk_jadwal"."updated" DESC, "atk_jadwal"."created" DESC LIMIT ?

SELECT "atk_pengajuan"."id", "atk_pengajuan"."jadwal_id", "atk_pengajuan"."unit_id", "atk_pengajuan"."no_surat", "atk_pengajuan"."keterangan", "atk_pengajuan"."progress", "atk_pengajuan"."hasil", "atk_pengajuan"."perbaikan", "atk_pengajuan"."is_terlambat", "atk_pengajuan"."is_aktif", "atk_pengajuan"."updated", "atk_pengajuan"."created" FROM "atk_pengajuan" WHERE ("atk_pengajuan"."jadwal_id" = ? AND "atk_pengajuan"."unit_id" = ?) ORDER BY "atk_pengajuan"."updated" DESC, "atk_pengajuan"."created" DESC LIMIT ?
